comments.body:
Okay, now I tested it without network and it's working.  My suspicion of `podman-registry` pulling down the image was correct.  I extended the go-bindings for it to support passing custom images which is now the tar file.

Once merged, I will apply the same changes to other e2e tests using `podman-registry` to use the local tar file instead of pulling the image down. Should help in the ongoing test speedups.

@edsantiago, mind taking another look?
